        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "IRS Publication 519 對於同一年度內既為非稅務居民又為稅務居民的非美籍人士,描述了雙重身分稅務年度,適用於許多抵達、離開及身分調整情況,而不僅限於跨州搬遷。",
