        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "若核發的證件因連動聯邦文件而有預期之外的短期有效期,更新時程可能影響國內航班、聯邦建築進入,以及搬家後其他可能依賴 REAL ID 的事項。",
        "Illinois Board of Higher Education directory page on campus liaisons supporting students under state tuition-equity provisions.": "Illinois 高等教育委員會關於支援依州學費平等規定學生之校園聯絡人的目錄頁面。",
        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Illinois 州務卿暫時訪客駕照(TVDL)頁面。ilsos.gov 對 curl HEAD 請求回傳 302 重新導向至其自身頁面,屬長期維運 .gov 網域上已知的假陰性;該網址已透過州務卿自家的搜尋索引確認。",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Illinois Student Assistance Commission 為非美籍學生提供的資源頁面,包含 RISE 法案及替代申請的背景。isac.org 對非瀏覽器請求回傳 403(反機器人);屬已知的假陰性。",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "移民身分(包括 Dreamer / DACA 身分)可能會對駕照與 REAL ID、專業執照(特別是護理及醫療類)、州內學費資格、SSN 相關要求,以及州稅申報產生重大影響。各州與聯邦法規不同,且時常變動。\n\nMoveSafe 並不能取代法律顧問。在依賴任何各州摘要前,請考慮諮詢持證移民律師。",
