        "J-1 specific. Frame as verify with the program sponsor and reference 22 CFR Part 62. Do not state that any specific category does or does not require sponsor pre-approval for a particular change. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "J-1 專屬。請以「向計劃贊助方核實並參考 22 CFR Part 62」表述。請勿陳述任何特定類別在特定變更下是否需贊助方事前核准。請避免使用 iOS SafeCopy 應避免清單。",
