        "Many nonimmigrant visa holders are not within the standard Medicare or Medicaid eligibility groups, and federal rules in this area have been changing. Destination-state Medicaid rules add another layer that may differ from origin-state rules.": "許多非移民簽證持有人不在 Medicare 或 Medicaid 標準資格族群內,且此領域的聯邦規則持續變動。目的地州的 Medicaid 規則增加了一層可能與出發州不同的規範。",
        "Many states require new residents to obtain a state driver's license within a specific period after becoming a resident.": "許多州要求新居民在成為居民後的特定期限內取得該州駕照。",
        "Mark as not verified": "標示為未核實",
        "Mark as verified": "標示為已核實",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for nonresidents using Form 1-NR/PY. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Massachusetts 稅務部關於使用 1-NR/PY 表格的非居民個人所得稅指南。mass.gov 對非瀏覽器請求回傳 403(Cloudflare);屬已知的假陰性。",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for part-year residents. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Massachusetts 稅務部關於部分年度居民個人所得稅的指南。mass.gov 對非瀏覽器請求回傳 403(Cloudflare);屬已知的假陰性。",
        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Massachusetts RMV 身分證明要求頁面,涵蓋 REAL ID、標準駕照,以及合法居留文件。mass.gov 對非瀏覽器請求回傳 403(Cloudflare);屬長期維運 .gov 託管州入口網站上已知的假陰性。",
        "Massachusetts identification (ID) requirements": "Massachusetts 身分證明(ID)要求",
        "May involve penalties or licensing consequences.": "可能涉及罰則或執照後果。",
        "Medicare.gov Get Started with Medicare": "Medicare.gov 開始使用 Medicare",
        "Minimum coverage, state-specific rules, and policy address updates.": "最低承保範圍、各州特定規則,以及保單地址更新。",
        "Missing a school or hospital onboarding requirement can delay clinical hours and graduation timing.": "未滿足學校或醫院的到職要求,可能延誤臨床時數累積及畢業時程。",
        "Missing a state motor vehicle deadline can create administrative or driving-related problems after relocation.": "錯過州車輛管理期限可能在搬遷後造成行政或駕駛相關問題。",
        "Missing source": "缺少資料來源",
        "Missing the transfer reporting steps at the new school, or letting the transfer release date and program start fall out of sync, can affect status maintenance and access to on-campus work.": "未在新校完成轉學報到步驟,或讓轉移釋放日與課程開始日不同步,可能影響身分維持及校內工作的取得。",
        "Mixed jurisdiction": "混合司法管轄",
        "MoveSafe checklist": "MoveSafe 檢查清單",
        "MoveSafe is a source-first checklist tool. It links you to official resources and highlights topics to verify. It does not provide legal advice.": "MoveSafe 是以資料來源為本的檢查清單工具。它會連結到官方資源,並標示需要核實的主題。本工具不提供法律意見。",
        "MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves. You can still build a checklist, but some items may not apply.": "MoveSafe 是為州際搬遷而設計的工具。您仍可建立檢查清單,但部分項目可能不適用。",
        "MoveSafe prefers official agency sources. Placeholder entries should be replaced with verified URLs before production use.": "MoveSafe 優先採用官方機構資料來源。正式使用前,佔位項目應替換為經核實的網址。",
        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe 根據公開可取得的資料來源,提供一般性法律及行政資訊。本工具不提供法律意見,亦不會建立律師委任關係,也不應作為您所在司法管轄區持證律師意見的替代品。法律及機構規則時常變動。在作出決定前,請務必向官方資料來源核實資訊。",
        "Moving across state lines? Know what to verify before you go.": "計劃跨州搬家?出發前先了解需要核實的事項。",
        "Moving for school": "為求學而搬家",
        "Moving for work": "為工作而搬家",
        "Moving from %1$@ to %2$@": "從 %1$@ 搬至 %2$@",
        "Moving from one state's aid program to another's may change which aid applications to consider and which documents to gather, and this can affect how to plan tuition and living costs at the destination.": "從一州的助學金計劃轉到另一州,可能改變要考量的申請類別及需準備的文件,進而影響目的地的學費及生活費規劃。",
        "Moving may change which state tax withholding forms apply, and remote work can create cross-state payroll questions.": "搬家可能改變適用的州稅扣繳表格;遠距工作則可能引發跨州薪資問題。",
        "Moving to another state for clinical rotations, externships, or supervised practice.": "為臨床輪訓、實習或受督導的執業而搬到另一州。",
        "NCLEX and license-by-endorsement steps can stall when documentation does not match a destination board's current rules, which can delay clinical placement, hire dates, and compact-state recognition.": "若文件不符合目的地委員會現行規則,NCLEX 應考及背書認可流程可能受阻,進而延誤臨床實習、到職日期,以及互認州的承認程序。",
        "NCLEX eligibility requirements": "NCLEX 應考資格要求",
        "NCSBN Licensure Compacts overview, including Nurse Licensure Compact context for non-citizen primary state of residency declarations.": "NCSBN 執照互認協議總覽,包含非美籍人士主要居住州宣告的護士執照互認協議背景。",
        "National Council of State Boards of Nursing licensure guidance page for background context across boards.": "National Council of State Boards of Nursing 執照指引頁面,提供跨委員會的背景資訊。",
        "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education page summarizing the Tuition Equality Act and the 2020 statute affecting dependent students of H-1B holders.": "New Jersey 高等教育部辦公室頁面,摘要學費平等法及 2020 年影響 H-1B 持有人受扶養學生的法律。",
        "New York DMV REAL ID page noting that an Enhanced ID is for U.S. citizens only and that REAL ID issued to applicants with temporary lawful status may expire with the federal document.": "New York DMV REAL ID 頁面,指出 Enhanced ID 僅限美籍人士使用,且核發給暫時合法身分申請人的 REAL ID 有效期可能與聯邦文件同時到期。",
        "New York DMV documentation guidance for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including REAL ID and standard credentials.": "New York DMV 對非美籍申請人的文件指引,包含 REAL ID 及標準證件。",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance FAQ on residency, nonresident filing, and telecommuting.": "New York 稅務及財政部關於居住身分、非居民申報及遠距工作的常見問題。",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance page on nonresident and part-year filing using Form IT-203.": "New York 稅務及財政部關於使用 IT-203 表格進行非居民及部分年度申報的頁面。",
        "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN licensure requirements page, which administers nursing licensure for New York.": "New York 州教育部專業辦公室 RN 執照要求頁面,該辦公室負責 New York 護理執照事務。",
        "No items match your filters": "沒有符合篩選條件的項目",
        "No source has been added yet for this item. Add an official source before relying on it.": "此項目尚未新增資料來源。依賴本項目前,請新增官方資料來源。",
        "No sources are attached to the items in this view.": "目前檢視的項目沒有附加任何資料來源。",
        "Non-Immigrant - Florida Department of Highway Safety and Motor Vehicles": "非移民 - Florida 公路安全與機動車輛部",
        "Nonimmigrant visa holders (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, and others) face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID (often tied to I-94 / visa dates), in-state tuition (most public universities classify F-1 students as out-of-state), professional licensure documentation, tax residency rules, and health-insurance options. USCIS also requires reporting any address change within 10 days via Form AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney, your school's DSO if on F-1, employer HR or immigration counsel if on a work visa, and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "非移民簽證持有人(F-1、H-1B、J-1、L-1、O-1 等)在駕照文件與 REAL ID(通常與 I-94 / 簽證日期相連)、州內學費(多數公立大學將 F-1 學生歸類為州外生)、專業執照文件、稅務居住身分規則,以及健康保險選擇等方面,各州規定不同。USCIS 也要求在地址變更後 10 天內透過 AR-11 表格通報。\n\nMoveSafe 並不能取代法律顧問。請考慮諮詢持證移民律師;若持 F-1 簽證,請聯絡學校的 DSO;若持工作簽證,請聯絡雇主人資或移民法律顧問;跨州報稅請諮詢合格稅務專業人員。",
        "Nonresident and part-year resident forms and instructions": "非居民及部分年度居民表格與說明",
