        "Registering or being recorded as registered, even by mistake, may create issues for naturalization, status renewal, or future immigration filings. The risk of an inadvertent record can depend on how a state's DMV workflow is designed.": "即便是因錯誤而登記或被記錄為已登記,日後也可能對歸化、身分延展,或未來的移民申請造成問題。意外登記的風險可能取決於該州 DMV 流程的設計方式。",
