        "Replace with an official URL from the origin state motor vehicle agency before relying on this item.": "依賴此項目前,請替換為出發州車輛管理機構的官方網址。",
        "Replace with official federal tax-authority guidance. Use only as general orientation; consult a qualified tax professional.": "請替換為官方聯邦稅務機關指引。僅供一般參考使用,請諮詢合格稅務專業人員。",
        "Replace with the destination state agriculture / animal-health agency. Some species, breeds, or vaccinations have specific entry rules.": "請替換為目的地州農業 / 動物衛生機構。某些物種、品種或疫苗有特定入境規則。",
