        "Some checklist items use placeholder sources. Replace with official sources before relying on them.": "部分清單項目使用佔位資料來源。依賴本資料前,請替換為官方資料來源。",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules.": "部分物品在不同州的規範可能不同,可能涉及州法、地方法規、聯邦法,或機構規則。",
        "Some items may be regulated differently across state lines and may involve state law, local ordinances, federal law, or agency rules. MoveSafe does not determine whether possession, transportation, or use is lawful in any specific situation. Verify directly with official sources and consult a licensed attorney or relevant agency if needed.": "部分項目在不同州的規範可能不同,可能涉及州法、地方法規、聯邦法,或機構規則。MoveSafe 不會判定在任何特定情況下持有、運輸或使用是否合法。請直接向官方資料來源核實,如有需要,請諮詢持證律師或相關機構。",
        "Some sources have not been verified recently. Check the official website before relying on them.": "部分資料來源近期尚未核實。依賴本資料前,請檢查官方網站。",
        "Some states issue driver licenses or state IDs to nonimmigrant visa applicants on a shortened renewal cycle that tracks the I-94 or an underlying federal document, instead of the multi-year cycle used for citizens. Fees, renewal timing, and steps after a status extension can differ between origin and destination states.": "部分州核發給非移民簽證申請人的駕照或州身分證採用較短的更新週期,與 I-94 或所依據的聯邦文件連動,而非適用於美國公民的多年週期。費用、更新時程,以及身分延展後的步驟,在出發州與目的地州之間可能不同。",
