        "Start fresh": "重新開始",
        "Starting work at a new worksite outside the LCA's MSA without an amended petition can affect status maintenance, and the timing of the amended petition filing matters for when the worker can begin at the new location.": "未辦理修正申請即於 LCA 所屬 MSA 以外的新工作地點開始工作,可能影響身分維持;修正申請的辦理時間將影響工作者何時可於新地點開始工作。",
        "State DMV document checklists for nonimmigrant visa applicants (F-1, J-1, H-1B, L-1, O-1 and similar) can differ from those used for U.S. citizens or lawful permanent residents. Accepted combinations of passport, visa, I-94, I-20 or DS-2019, and I-797 or employer letter may vary, and some states ask for an SSN card or an SSA ineligibility letter.": "州 DMV 對非移民簽證申請人(F-1、J-1、H-1B、L-1、O-1 等)的文件清單,可能與適用於美國公民或合法永久居民的清單不同。接受的護照、簽證、I-94、I-20 或 DS-2019,以及 I-797 或雇主信函等文件組合可能不同;部分州會要求 SSN 卡或 SSA 不符資格證明信。",
        "State University of New York Board of Trustees policy on residency for tuition purposes, including which visa categories can establish New York domicile. suny.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing state university system domain.": "State University of New York 董事會關於學費目的居住身分的政策,包含哪些簽證類別可建立 New York 住所。suny.edu 對非瀏覽器請求回傳 403(Cloudflare);屬長期維運州立大學系統網域上已知的假陰性。",
        "State filing requirements, part-year residency, remote work implications.": "州報稅要求、部分年度居民身分,以及遠距工作的影響。",
        "State grant and scholarship programs each have their own rules about whether non-citizen students may be considered, what application form (FAFSA, a state alternative, or an institutional form) is used, and what documentation is needed.": "各州的助學金及獎學金計劃各自訂定規則,包括是否考量非美籍學生、使用哪種申請表格(FAFSA、州替代表格,或院校表格),以及所需文件。",
        "State labor law basics (paid sick leave, breaks, final pay rules)": "州勞動法基本事項(有薪病假、休息時間、離職薪資規則)",
        "State law": "州法",
        "State residency basics": "州居住身分基本事項",
        "State tax filing can apply even when income is earned remotely. Rules differ by state.": "即使收入來自遠距工作,州報稅仍可能適用。各州規則不同。",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. A person treated as a nonresident alien on the federal return may still be a resident, part-year resident, or nonresident for state purposes depending on domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors. States may or may not conform to federal income tax treaty exclusions.": "州稅居住身分依各州自身規則認定,可能與聯邦稅居住身分不同。在聯邦報稅表上被視為非稅務居民外國人之人,於州稅而言可能仍依住所、實際居住天數、雇主所在地及其他因素被視為居民、部分年度居民或非居民。各州是否遵循聯邦所得稅協定排除條款不一。",
        "State tax residency is determined under each state's own rules, which may differ from federal tax residency. Domicile, days of physical presence, employer location, and other factors can each play a role.": "州稅居住身分依各州自身規則認定,可能與聯邦稅居住身分不同。住所、實際居住天數、雇主所在地,以及其他因素,均可能起作用。",
        "State tax withholding, labor law basics, remote work considerations.": "州稅扣繳、勞動法基本事項,以及遠距工作的考量。",
        "States and individual public colleges and universities use different tuition-classification rules for non-citizens, including how prior in-state high school attendance, current immigration status, and a parent's residency are considered.": "各州及各公立大學對非美籍學生的學費身分認定規則不同,包括如何考量先前州內高中就讀經歷、現行移民身分,以及父母的居住情況。",
        "States may require proof of identity, residency, lawful presence, school documents, or other paperwork.": "各州可能要求提供身分證明、居住證明、合法居留證明、學校文件,或其他文件。",
