        "This checklist is based on your selected categories and available source data. It may not include every requirement that applies to your situation.": "此清單根據您所選的類別及現有資料來源資料而產生,可能未涵蓋適用於您情況的所有要求。",
        "This checklist is not a legal conclusion. Verify with official sources and consult a licensed professional where appropriate.": "此清單並非法律結論。請向官方資料來源核實,並在適當情況下諮詢持證專業人員。",
        "This source has not been verified in more than a year. Treat as stale and verify directly with the official source.": "此資料來源已逾一年未核實。請視為過時資料,並直接向官方資料來源核實。",
        "This source has not been verified in more than six months. Check the official website before relying on it.": "此資料來源已逾六個月未核實。依賴本資料前,請先檢查官方網站。",
