        "Travel documentation if flying with a pet": "搭機攜帶寵物的旅行文件",
        "Treating an intra-MSA worksite change as a full new petition can create unnecessary cost and timing risk, while assuming portability rules apply without checking the MSA boundaries can lead to status questions later.": "將同 MSA 內的工作地點變更視為完全新申請,可能造成不必要的成本及時程風險;但未核對 MSA 範圍即假設適用變動規則,日後可能引發身分問題。",
