        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "USCIS 存檔頁面,摘要 2015 年 Simeio Solutions 最終指引,以及工作地點移至 MSA 之外觸發 LCA 修正的情況。",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that a U.S. Postal Service change-of-address request does not change a record with USCIS and that USPS does not forward USCIS mail. A destination-state DMV address update is also a separate step from the federal AR-11 filing.": "USCIS 指引一般指出,美國郵政機關的地址變更申請並不會變更 USCIS 的紀錄,USPS 也不會轉寄 USCIS 信件。目的地州 DMV 的地址更新亦與聯邦 AR-11 通報屬不同步驟。",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "USCIS 指引一般指出,H-1B 工作者若於現行 LCA 所屬同一 MSA 或預定就業區域內移至新工作地點,通常不需要新的 LCA 或修正 H-1B 申請,但現行 LCA 仍可能需在新工作地點張貼。聯邦 AR-11 地址變更要求仍適用於該工作者。",
        "USCIS newsroom alert describing the online change-of-address tool and clarifying that USPS forwarding does not change a USCIS record.": "USCIS 新聞室公告,說明線上地址變更工具,並澄清 USPS 郵件轉寄不會變更 USCIS 紀錄。",
        "USCIS umbrella page on the federal change-of-address requirement, including the online change-of-address tool.": "USCIS 關於聯邦地址變更要求的綜合頁面,內含線上地址變更工具。",
        "USPS Mail Forwarding / Change of Address": "USPS 郵件轉寄 / 地址變更",
        "USPS mail-forwarding page; referenced to clarify that USPS change-of-address does not substitute for federal AR-11 filing per USCIS guidance.": "USPS 郵件轉寄頁面;參考此頁以澄清依 USCIS 指引,USPS 地址變更不可取代聯邦 AR-11 通報。",
        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "依據 22 CFR Part 62,J-1 計劃贊助方負責維護每位交流訪客的 SEVIS 紀錄並監督其活動地點。若搬家變更住處、活動地點或接待機構,一般會觸發交流訪客向贊助方通報及贊助方更新 SEVIS 的義務。",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "依據 USCIS 在 Matter of Simeio Solutions(2015)後的指引,若 H-1B 工作者的工作地點移至現行 Labor Condition Application(LCA)所列大都會統計區(MSA)或預定就業區域之外,一般構成重大變更,需辦理新的 LCA 並修正 H-1B 申請。",
        "Understand how the destination state defines residency": "了解目的地州如何定義居住身分",
        "Undocumented Student Liaisons - Illinois Board of Higher Education": "無證件學生聯絡人 - Illinois 高等教育委員會",
        "University of California admissions page on the AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption, noting that most nonimmigrant visa holders such as F-1 or J-1 generally cannot establish California residency for tuition purposes.": "University of California 入學頁面,關於 AB 540 非居民學費豁免,指出多數非移民簽證持有人(例如 F-1 或 J-1)一般無法為學費目的建立 California 居住身分。",
        "Update employment paperwork and state tax forms": "更新就業文件及州稅表格",
        "Use do not assume language. Do not state that USPS or DMV updates can substitute for AR-11 (USCIS guidance says they generally do not). Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "請使用「請勿假設」的措辭。請勿陳述 USPS 或 DMV 更新可取代 AR-11(USCIS 指引指出一般不可)。請避免使用 iOS SafeCopy 應避免清單(法律結論式措辭及與規避罰則相關的措辭)。",
        "Vaccination, licensing, breed restrictions, housing pet policies.": "疫苗、登記、品種限制,以及住房寵物政策。",
