        "Whether a closer connection exception or a tax-treaty tie-breaker rule may apply": "更密切聯繫例外或稅收協定平衡條款是否可能適用",
        "Whether a first-year choice or a tax-treaty election can change the analysis": "首年選擇或稅收協定選擇是否可改變評估結果",
