        "Whether a license issued to a non-citizen may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "核發給非美籍人士的執照,其更新週期是否可能因連動聯邦文件而較短",
        "Whether a license issued to a visa holder may have a shorter renewal cycle tied to a federal document": "核發給簽證持有人的執照,其更新週期是否可能因連動聯邦文件而較短",
        "Whether a move that includes a change of school or program site requires additional SEVIS steps beyond an address update": "若搬家涉及學校或計劃地點變更,是否需要在地址更新外辦理額外的 SEVIS 步驟",
