        "Whether an SSN is required to apply, and whether an ITIN, an SSA ineligibility letter, or an affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "申辦是否需要 SSN,以及 ITIN、SSA 不符資格證明信,或書面聲明書是否可作為替代",
        "Whether an exempt-individual rule (for certain F, J, M, Q categories) may apply and for how many years": "豁免個人規則(適用於某些 F、J、M、Q 類)是否可能適用,以及適用幾年",
        "Whether any active USCIS receipt number has its own e-Notification or online-account address that needs to be checked": "任何使用中的 USCIS 受理編號是否有其自身的電子通知或線上帳戶地址需要檢查",
        "Whether any category-specific rules (research scholar, professor, intern, trainee, physician, au pair, and others) add steps that the sponsor must approve": "任何類別特有規則(研究學者、教授、實習生、受訓人員、醫師、互惠生等)是否增加贊助方須核准的步驟",
        "Whether any change in job duties, hours, or wage triggers a separate amendment analysis even when the worksite stays in the same MSA": "即使工作地點維持在同一 MSA,任何工作職責、工時或薪資的變更是否會觸發另行的修正評估",
