        "Whether the J-1 sponsor has been notified within 10 days of any change in U.S. address, telephone, or email": "美國地址、電話或電子郵件的任何變更,是否已於 10 天內通知 J-1 贊助方",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the I-94, the visa, or an I-797 or I-20 or DS-2019, and how renewal works after a status extension": "REAL ID 有效期是否可能與 I-94、簽證,或 I-797、I-20 或 DS-2019 連動,以及身分延展後的更新方式",
        "Whether the REAL ID expiration date may be tied to the underlying federal document": "REAL ID 有效期是否可能與所依據的聯邦文件連動",
