        "Whether the board accepts background-check results processed under your current status": "委員會是否接受依您現行身分處理的背景調查結果",
        "Whether the calendar-year count of days under the Substantial Presence Test meets the federal threshold for the current year": "依實質居留測試計算的本年度日曆年居留天數是否達到聯邦門檻",
        "Whether the current nonimmigrant status appears on the current HealthCare.gov lawfully present list": "現行非移民身分是否在 HealthCare.gov 目前的合法居留清單中",
