        "Whether the destination Board of Nursing requires an SSN at application, and whether an ITIN, attestation, or affidavit is accepted as an alternative": "目的地護理委員會在申辦時是否要求 SSN,以及 ITIN、書面聲明或聲明書是否可作為替代",
        "Whether the destination DMV requires original documents and current address proofs, and whether copies or translations are accepted": "目的地 DMV 是否要求正本文件及目前的地址證明,以及是否接受副本或翻譯本",
        "Whether the destination address is being reported to the DSO or J-1 sponsor within 10 days of the move": "目的地地址是否已在搬家後 10 天內向 DSO 或 J-1 贊助方通報",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return": "在目的地州報稅表要求 SSN 之處,該州是否接受 ITIN",
        "Whether the destination state accepts an ITIN where an SSN is requested on its return, and whether a separate state tax ID is offered": "在目的地州報稅表要求 SSN 之處,該州是否接受 ITIN,以及是否提供另行的州稅務識別號",
        "Whether the destination state conforms to federal income tax treaty exclusions for nonresident aliens, or taxes that income at the state level": "目的地州是否遵循聯邦對非稅務居民外國人所得稅協定排除條款,或在州層級對該所得課稅",
        "Whether the destination state considers you a resident": "目的地州是否將您視為居民",
        "Whether the destination state defines residency by domicile, by days of physical presence, or by a combination": "目的地州是依住所、實際居住天數,或兩者組合來認定居住身分",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity or high-school-attendance provision that could apply, and what documentation it requires": "目的地州是否有可能適用的學費平等或高中就讀條款,以及該條款要求哪些文件",
        "Whether the destination state has a tuition-equity policy that may apply, and what documentation it requires": "目的地州是否有可能適用的學費平等政策,以及該政策要求哪些文件",
