        "Whether the destination state has different tax withholding forms": "目的地州是否有不同的稅務扣繳表格",
        "Whether the destination state has elected the CHIPRA option to cover lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals without a federal waiting period": "目的地州是否已選擇 CHIPRA 選項,在無聯邦等待期的情況下承保合法居留之兒童及孕婦",
        "Whether the destination state imposes a minimum remaining stay on the I-94 before issuing a credential": "目的地州在核發證件前是否要求 I-94 上剩餘居留期達到一定下限",
