        "Whether the destination state offers any state-funded coverage for people not eligible for the federal marketplace": "目的地州是否為不符合聯邦保險市集資格的人士提供州經費保險",
        "Whether the destination state offers any voting that is open to non-citizens (for example, certain local elections), and how that may interact with federal voter rolls": "目的地州是否提供開放給非美籍人士參與的投票(例如某些地方選舉),以及這可能如何與聯邦選民名冊互動",
        "Whether the destination state operates a non-FAFSA aid application for students who cannot file a FAFSA": "目的地州是否為無法提交 FAFSA 的學生提供非 FAFSA 助學金申請",
        "Whether the destination state operates state-funded SNAP, TANF, or cash-assistance programs that may apply during the federal waiting period": "目的地州是否營運可能適用於聯邦等待期間的州經費 SNAP、TANF 或現金援助計劃",
        "Whether the destination state participates in the Nurse Licensure Compact and how that interacts with non-citizen documentation": "目的地州是否參與護士執照互認協議,以及其與非美籍人士文件的互動方式",
        "Whether the destination state recognizes your specific visa category as one that may establish a domicile for tuition purposes": "目的地州是否將您的特定簽證類別視為可為學費目的建立住所的類別",
        "Whether the destination state requires a Social Security card or an SSA ineligibility letter, and how the visa category interacts with SSN issuance timing": "目的地州是否要求 Social Security 卡或 SSA 不符資格證明信,以及簽證類別如何與 SSN 核發時程互動",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace": "目的地州是使用 HealthCare.gov 還是經營自有的州自營保險市集",
        "Whether the destination state uses HealthCare.gov or runs its own state-based marketplace with separate documentation rules": "目的地州是使用 HealthCare.gov 還是經營自有的州自營保險市集,並訂有獨立的文件規則",
        "Whether the destination state uses the CHIPRA/ICHIA option to remove the waiting period for children, pregnant people, or both": "目的地州是否採用 CHIPRA/ICHIA 選項取消兒童、孕婦,或兩者的等待期",
