        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney about timing renewals around an extension or change of status": "在身分延展或變更期間規劃更新時程時,是否應諮詢您的指定學校官員、雇主移民聯絡人,或持證移民律師",
        "Whether you should consult your designated school official, employer immigration contact, or a licensed immigration attorney before applying": "在申辦前是否應諮詢您的指定學校官員、雇主移民聯絡人,或持證移民律師",
        "Whether you should speak with your prescriber or pharmacist": "是否應與您的處方醫師或藥師討論",
